title: Chinese spacecraft Shenzhou-8 re-docks with prototype space lab Tiangong-1
description: BEIJING， Nov. 14 (Xinhua) -- China's Shenzhou-8 unmanned spacecraft re-docked with the Tiangong-1， a module of the country's planned space lab， Monday evening， according to the mission's control center.
cleanContent:
The graphics shows the procedure of the second docking between Shenzhou-8 spacecraft and Tiangong-1 space lab module on Nov. 14， 2011. (Xinhua/Lu Zhe)

BEIJING, Nov. 14 (Xinhua) -- China's Shenzhou-8 unmanned spacecraft re-docked with the Tiangong-1, a module of the country's planned space lab, Monday evening, according to the mission's control center. | |
